Keller Williams Sun Valley Southern Idaho

data.description: Wonderful Family Home where everyone can spread out and have their own space. When it is time to gather, there is a lot of room to meet in the middle! This established home is in a sought-after neighborhood and is more spacious than it looks from the curb. Features you will enjoy: 6 bedrooms, spa-like master bathroom with tub & walk-in shower, cook's kitchen with reverse osmosis & 2 pantries, oodles of storage, solar panels for reduced power bill, main floor laundry with utility sink, 3 car garage with small office, formal and informal dining spaces, newer high efficiency HVAC, water softener, sunken living room, gas fireplace, surround sound in the family room, fully concreted enclosed RV pad, security system, established garden, and backyard with enough room to toss a football. The owner has been working on this house for the past couple of years to make it beautiful, efficient & comfortable. Now it is your turn to enjoy the amenities.
